dcterms:description: Real data of the deployments of a variety of services from Amazon AWS, containing 4966 labeled deployments and 27590 unlabeled deployments. The dataset includes metrics such as Threads, CPU usage, and Memory usage, with 8 meta-data features.
dcterms:title: Real data of cloud services

dcterms:description: A dataset containing 4966 labeled deployments, where labels were aggregated using three approaches: Hard Labels, Soft Labels, and Naive Labels. The dataset includes 234,508 time series with 288 anomalies.
dcterms:title: Hard-Labeled set

dcterms:description: A dataset containing 4966 labeled deployments, where labels were aggregated using Soft Labels. The dataset includes 234,508 time series with 544 anomalies.
dcterms:title: Soft-Labeled set

dcterms:description: A dataset containing 4688 labeled deployments, where labels were aggregated using Naive Labels. The dataset includes 220,320 time series with 544 anomalies.
dcterms:title: Naive-Labeled set

dcterms:description: A dataset containing 27,590 unlabeled deployments. This dataset is used for training semi-supervised methods.
dcterms:title: Unlabeled set

dcterms:description: A dataset containing 30K+ deployments with 1.2M+ time series from Amazon, used for evaluating the MELODY framework.
dcterms:title: 30K+ deployments with 1.2M+ time series from Amazon
